Package: LineageDE
Title: LineageDE: Differential Gene Expression Testing Along Lineages
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Apeksha Singh
Maintainer: Apeksha Singh <apekshasingh@g.ucla.edu>
Description: Gene expression dynamics resulting from pseudotime reconstruction are fit using a negative binomial generalized additive model (NB-GAM).
    Using the NB-GAM, differential expression is determined between different conditions or lineages (see convertInput).
    Implemented to accept multiple samples of psuedotime input for which labels are permuted to construct a null distribution.
